nice Shanghai style restaurant with good food at reasonable

Lunch Set is quite expensive while the portion is barely enough.
Too much bones in the chicken and the bowl shape is not user friendly
Portion is super small. Taste okay except the dumpling. Skin too thick.

Poorly service especially around 8pm. It is not my first time here. It appears they are preparing to close around that time. They start taking away condiments when you are just starting your meal. Xiao lung bao no vinegar. Ask for it they say WAIT!! They make you feel like a kid, not a customer, expecting you to finish food, pay for 10% service charge ( fixed in bill so no need to exert energy for good service). How would you like to stop by and try their service?! Char chan teng better service in comparison. The food is good though.

result.name: 上海姥姥

reviews.text: 服務尚可，位置不近地鐵，消費略貴，食物質素良好，商場舖，裝修不錯。
食物馬虎，點餐後不用一分鍾已上菜，炒飯是暖的明顯一早炒好待上，要留住食客請專重食材
舖頭位於商場內，中午食晏人流較多。坐位及環境舒適，午市有客飯提供，但加一後差不多$100/位，略貴。至於食味不錯，份量適中。
推介麻辣雞肉拌麵，放在拌麵上的葱很香
環境在商場入面，尚算舒服。食物算幾好。價錢可以。總算80分
